#### Go to meeting(all) to get id, you can choose one of those id

![image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/af91a5b6-7ea8-453b-914d-cb11153f26e7)

#### Finally go to `Add participant`, you can change what ever name you want </br>

Paste id to this filed: `"custom_participant_id": "bbb04ac2-2fc7-46b3-b4d5-f5f3555df10e",`</br>

You can generate viewer and host token by changing this field: `"preset_name": "livestream_viewer" -> viewer` or `"preset_name": "livestream_host" -> host`
